hc.server.ui

Class ClientSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • hc.server.ui.ClientSession

  • public class ClientSession
extends Object
    a ClientSession instance will be created before ProjectContext.EVENT_SYS_MOBILE_LOGIN, and will be released by server after ProjectContext.EVENT_SYS_MOBILE_LOGOUT.

    a ProjectContext instance will be created before ProjectContext.EVENT_SYS_PROJ_STARTUP, and will be released after ProjectContext.EVENT_SYS_PROJ_SHUTDOWN.

    invoke ProjectContext.getClientSession() to get this instance for current session.

    it is thread safe.
    Since:
    7.7
